CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1967, pg. 1 & 3 reads: "...Negroes of leadership status and plain citizens jammed Ebenezer Church to hear the controversial Stokely Carmichael, director of SNCC, speak...-Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Stokely Carmichael (Kwame Ture) speaking at podium in Ebenezer Baptist Church
